public class CaseEvalList
extends java.util.TreeSet<CaseEvaluation>
implements CBRTerm

Data structure containing a set of CaseEvaluation objects, that holds a case and a object that represents an evaluation of the case. The structure will keep a ascending order of the cases according their evaluation.
